{"word":"H3104 - יֹובֵל - yôwbêl - yo-bale' - Jubile","slug":"H3104","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יֹובֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yôwbêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yo-bale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jubile"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05D1;&#x05DC;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D9;&#x05D5;&#x05D1;&#x05DC; - yo&#x0302;be&#x0302;l  yo&#x0302;be&#x0302;l</b> - <i>yo-bale', yo-bale'</i><p/>Apparently from <a href=\"#/H2986\">H2986</a>; the <i>blast</i> of a horn (from its <i>continuous</i> sound); specifically the <i>signal</i> of the silver trumpets; hence the instrument itself and the festival thus introduced: - jubile, ram&rsquo;s horn, trumpet."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H180\">H180</a>, <a href=\"#/H2981\">H2981</a>, <a href=\"#/H2986\">H2986</a>, <a href=\"#/H2988\">H2988</a>, <a href=\"#/H2989\">H2989</a>, <a href=\"#/H2990\">H2990</a>, <a href=\"#/H2991\">H2991</a>, <a href=\"#/H3105\">H3105</a>, <a href=\"#/H3106\">H3106</a>, <a href=\"#/H8398\">H8398</a>, <a href=\"#/H944\">H944</a>"}]}